GeDocumentTabbedPane - Class in view
public class GeDocumentTabbedPane extends JTabbedPane implements Observer
A custom JTabbedPane that visually represents GeDocuments in InternalFrame.
It holds a model of project whose GeDocuments it represents,
and a list of PageTabbedPane objects that it displays.
GeDocumentTabbedPane(Project) - Constructor for class view.GeDocumentTabbedPane
Creates a new GeDocumentTabbedPane instance having a Project passed to it, and if project already has GeDocuments, it adds them manually.
